Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:07.54,Default,Mihara,0,0,0,,{TIME:126001,127544}Increase the speed!{NOTE:もっとスピード上げて！}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.54,0:02:11.17,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{TIME:127544,131173}But if I raise it any further, the speed will be 80 km/h.{NOTE:でも、これ以上上げると時速80キロになるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.17,0:02:12.71,Default,Mihara,0,0,0,,{TIME:131173,132716}I don't care.{NOTE:構わないからやってよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.51,0:02:17.80,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{TIME:135510,137804}You really are a superhuman, Captain.{NOTE:まったく超人的だわ、キャプテンは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.13,0:02:19.89,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{TIME:139139,139890}Here goes.{NOTE:いいわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.89,0:02:20.72,Default,Mihara,0,0,0,,{TIME:139890,140724}Okay.{NOTE:オッケー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:38.82,Alternative,Mihara,0,0,0,,{TIME:157699,158825}Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.82,0:02:41.91,Alternative,Mihara,0,0,0,,{TIME:158825,161912}I will become a receiver\Nthat can compete against your spikes.{NOTE:私はあなたのスパイクに対抗できるレシーバに成る。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:44.49,Alternative,Mihara,0,0,0,,{TIME:161912,164498}I've been practicing like hell until today.{NOTE:今日まで血の滲むような練習を重ねてきたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.49,0:02:47.33,Alternative,Mihara,0,0,0,,{TIME:164498,167334}I'll counter your ball with these hands.{NOTE:きっとこの手であなたのボールを受けて見せるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:50.71,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:168627,170712}I've never seen such training before.{NOTE:あんな凄い練習見たことないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.71,0:02:52.67,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:170712,172673}That in itself is a bit unsettling.{NOTE:それはもう恐ろしいぐらいよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:53.92,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:172673,173924}Unbelievable.{NOTE:XXXな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:58.55,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:173924,178553}She set that machine at speed of no less than 80 km/h.{NOTE:あんな機会で練習されたんじゃ何しろね、時速80km/h。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:02:59.47,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:178553,179471}Do you realize it?{NOTE:分かる？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:02.89,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:179471,182891}It's twice as fast as the girls' record spike.{NOTE:女子の最高のスパイクの倍以上のスピードなのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.89,0:03:04.18,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:182891,184184}Wow, that's a shock.{NOTE:わ、ショック。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:07.56,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:184184,187562}So no matter how strong our spike is, she'll receive it like it's nothing.{NOTE:じゃ、どんな強いスパイクだって軽くレシーブされちゃうじゃないの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:09.89,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:187562,189898}Don't make such a miserable voice.{NOTE:そんな情けない声出さないでよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.89,0:03:13.11,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:189898,193110}It only means that we must practice more and harder.{NOTE:向こうがそうなら、こっちはそれ以上の練習すればいいのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:14.02,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:193110,194027}That's what I'd like to do.{NOTE:やりがいがあるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.07,0:03:16.98,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:195070,196988}Let's start with it right now.{NOTE:かえってファイトがXXきたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:22.86,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:198740,202869}But it's just Mihara Yumiko, their captain,\Nwho can do such receive, right?{NOTE:でもそれだけのレシーブができるのはキャプテンの三原ゆみこだけでしょ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:26.12,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:202869,206123}Then I suggest we just aim at other people in her team.{NOTE:だったら、その他の人を狙って打っていけばいいわけよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:31.37,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:206123,211378}In principle, you're right, but I'd prefer if the new Fujimi High School team would fight honestly.{NOTE:それはそうですけど、富士見高校チームの新しい力を真っ正面からぶつけてみたいんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:32.83,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:211920,212838}Right, Kozue?{NOTE:ね、こずえ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:34.42,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:213714,214423}Sure.{NOTE:え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:37.25,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:214423,217259}I don't believe that speed alone is decisive.{NOTE:スピードだけでは破壊力だとは思わないけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:39.01,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:217259,219010}But how are we going to attack?{NOTE:ども、どう攻めればいいか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:40.97,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:219010,220971}Kozue, you, of all people?{NOTE:しっかりしてよ、こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:43.76,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:220971,223765}Don't forget you were the captain of our national team.{NOTE:オールジャパンのキャプテンだったこと忘れないで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.76,0:03:46.85,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:223765,226852}Yeah. We'll follow you anywhere, Captain.{NOTE:そうよ。私達はキャプテンについていくわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:49.43,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:226852,229438}Naka, stop calling me captain.{NOTE:ナカ、キャプテンて言うのは止めてよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:51.31,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:229438,231314}We're not in middle school anymore.{NOTE:中学時代だ。もう違うのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:54.60,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:231314,234609}All right, all right. At any rate, we're counting on you.{NOTE:いいから、いいから。私達は頼りにしてるんだから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:55.90,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:234609,235902}Right, girls?{NOTE:ね、皆？そうでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:56.98,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:235902,236987}Yeah!{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:03:59.36,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:237904,239364}All right, time to practice.{NOTE:さ、練習の時間よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:00.53,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:239364,240532}Let's do our best.{NOTE:頑張っていこう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:03.41,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:240532,243410}It's Fujimi High School team's rebirth!{NOTE:富士見高校チームは新しく生まれ変わったのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:05.12,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:243410,245120}– Work hard!\N– Fight with all you have!{NOTE:—頑張ろう！\\N—ファイトで行こう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:08.41,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:247289,248415}Come on, Captain.{NOTE:ほら、キャプテン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:10.20,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:248999,250208}– Yeah.\N– Let's go.{NOTE:—うん。\\N—行こう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:40.36,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:279446,280363}Ah, I'm sorry!{NOTE:あ、ごめん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:43.82,Alternative,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:282032,283825}Spike machine.{NOTE:スパイク・マシン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:47.12,Alternative,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:283825,287120}They practice receives by launching a ball twice as fast as world's record.{NOTE:機会で倍以上のスピードボールを打ち出してレシーブの練習。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:50.33,Alternative,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:288246,290332}To counter that receive, we need…{NOTE:このレシーブを破るためには…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:52.20,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:291249,292209}All right, let's wrap it up.{NOTE:はい、それまで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:54.96,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:293502,294961}Ayuhara-san, Takeichi-san, Hayakawa-san.{NOTE:鮎原さん、武市さん、早川さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:55.42,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:294961,295420}Yes ma'am.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:57.42,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:295420,297422}The rest, short break.{NOTE:他の人はしばらく休んで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:04:58.08,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:297422,298089}Yes ma'am.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.08,0:05:04.67,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:298089,304679}What do you think we need to counter Misawa Academy's reception trained with a spike machine?{NOTE:ね、スパイク・マシンを使って練習してる美沢学院のレシーブを破るためには何が必要だと思う？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:10.31,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:309309,310310}Uhm…{NOTE:あの…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:11.56,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:310310,311561}What is it, Takeichi-san?{NOTE:何、武市さん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:15.23,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:311561,315232}Professor, you just told "Misawa Academy's reception"…{NOTE:今先生は美沢学院のレシーブって言われましたが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:17.44,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:315232,317442}But the problem is Captain Mihara alone.{NOTE:…問題は三原キャプテン一人です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:20.69,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:317442,320695}I thought to aim at her teammates instead.{NOTE:三原キャプテン以外を狙って行くとも作戦だと思います。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:25.90,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:320695,325909}It may not be the most honorable strategy, but I think it's better than forceful pushing.{NOTE:消極的かもしれませんが、力で押すだけは作戦じゃないって私は思います。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:27.16,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:325909,327160}I agree.{NOTE:その通りね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:30.78,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:327160,330789}But I'm sure it's not just their captain that practices on that spike machine.{NOTE:でもキャプテン以外も当然スパイク・マシンで練習してるでしょ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:33.50,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:330789,333500}We shouldn't underestimate the other players.{NOTE:その力を軽く見ることはできないわ。}
