Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:54.48,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:772272,774482}Now to only make it faster. All right, resume.{NOTE:もっと早くできれば…さ、もう一度。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:56.81,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:775817,776818}Here goes!{NOTE:行くわよ！}
Comment: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:10.70,Default,Chapter,0,0,0,,{TIME:790707,790707}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:14.29,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{TIME:793543,794294}Okay, good.{NOTE:いいわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:19.79,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:797045,799799}A "machine gun attack" to counter the spike machine.{NOTE:スパイク・マシンに対するマシンガン・アタックできたし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:21.71,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:799799,801718}Misawa Academy doesn't stand a chance against us.{NOTE:もう美沢学院なんたに負けないわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:22.71,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:801718,802719}We won't get beaten.{NOTE:XXXだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:27.26,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:805179,807265}But we're not finished yet.{NOTE:でも、未だ感性じゃないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:30.97,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:807265,810977}We still can't do it under 5 seconds like Professor Shimizu told us to.{NOTE:清水先生の言う5秒いないのアタッカーまだできてないもの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:32.93,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:810977,812937}It's fine as long as we master it before the match.{NOTE:試合までに完成すれば大丈夫よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.93,0:13:34.43,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:812937,814439}Everyone's into it.{NOTE:皆はりきってんだから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:37.85,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:814439,817859}With us, the Fujimi High School volleyball team was born anew.{NOTE:富士見高校バレー部は私達が新しいチームになったわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:40.77,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:819444,820778}Captain, Midori!{NOTE:キャプテン！みどり！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:42.48,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:820778,822488}Here you again with your "captain"…{NOTE:又「キャプテン」だなんて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:44.19,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:822488,824198}Hey, hey. You gotta see it yourself.{NOTE:ね、ちょっと、ちょっと。これ見てよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.19,0:13:45.19,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:824198,825199}Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.19,0:13:47.24,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:825199,827243}They're letters of resignation\Nfrom Takeichi-san and Ishikawa-san.{NOTE:武市さんと石川さんの退部届け。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:48.61,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:827243,828619}Huh!?{NOTE:え？！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:49.41,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:828619,829412}What's the reason?{NOTE:理由は？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:52.12,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:829412,832123}They just left it in the club room and departed without a word.{NOTE:今ね、黙って部室に置いてったのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:54.25,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:832123,834250}Maybe because she was removed from the "machine gun" team?{NOTE:マシンガン・アタックを外されたせいかしら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:56.04,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:834250,836044}Ah, and Ishikawa-san went along…{NOTE:あ、それで石川さんも一緒に？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:14:00.00,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:836044,840006}Having regular players quit right before the game is pretty troublesome…{NOTE:困ったわね。試合の前にしてレギュラーが二人も抜けるなんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:01.17,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:840006,841174}Ah, Kozue!{NOTE:あ、こずえ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:06.01,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:844719,846012}Takeichi-san!{NOTE:武市さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.84,0:14:10.05,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:848848,850058}Takeichi-san!{NOTE:武市さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:11.35,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:850767,851351}Ayuhara-san—{NOTE:鮎原さん—}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:13.56,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:851351,853561}Why did you quit the club? Why?{NOTE:どうしてバレー部止めるの？どうしてなの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:17.39,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:853561,857398}We promised to play together in the new volleyball club…{NOTE:新しくなったバレー部で一緒にやって行こうって約束したのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:18.90,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:857398,858900}I don't want to anymore.{NOTE:私はもう止めたの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:20.19,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:858900,860193}I'd like to keep the reason to myself.{NOTE:理由は言いたくないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:21.81,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:860193,861819}Takeichi-san…{NOTE:武市さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:23.86,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:861819,863863}Do I really have to tell why?{NOTE:どうしても聞きたいって言うの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:25.07,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:863863,865073}All right, fine.{NOTE:まいいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.07,0:14:29.24,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:865073,869243}It's awkward for us second years if you, a first year, become our captain.{NOTE:あなたがキャプテンに成った時、私達二年生がいるとやりにくいでしょ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:31.20,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:869243,871204}But I'm not even your captain.{NOTE:私はキャプテンじゃないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:32.99,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:871204,872997}You have the skill.{NOTE:あなたには実力があるし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:35.79,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:872997,875792}You're in the center of the current team.{NOTE:今のチームあなたを中心に纏まっている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:38.04,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:875792,878044}It's only natural for you to be our captain.{NOTE:当然キャプテンに成るべきよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:40.21,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:878044,880213}And it's awkward for you to have us around.{NOTE:二年生がいたらあなたもやりにくいし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:45.34,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:881005,885343}And to be perfectly honest, I don't want to play under a freshman.{NOTE:それに正直言って、一年生のキャプテンの下に成るとっても私にも抵抗があるね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:47.88,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:885343,887887}I never wanted to become the captain…{NOTE:一年生の私がキャプテンに成るなんて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:52.47,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:887887,892475}The current Fujimi High School team needs you to become its captain.{NOTE:今の富士見高校チームに必要なのはあなたがキャプテンに成ることよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.47,0:14:54.06,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:892475,894060}It doesn't need us.{NOTE:私達じゃないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:15:00.06,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:897522,900066}You should think less about me and more about the team.{NOTE:あなたはチームのことを考えてればいいの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:06.86,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:905571,906864}I see.{NOTE:そう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:08.86,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:906864,908866}It can't be helped.{NOTE:そう言うなら仕方ないわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:11.16,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:908866,911160}Professor, what should we do?{NOTE:先生。どうすればいいんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.16,0:15:12.57,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:911160,912578}Are we going to let them go like that?{NOTE:このままでいいんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.57,0:15:13.99,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:912578,913996}There's nothing we can do.{NOTE:仕方ないわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.99,0:15:16.54,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:913996,916541}We have to do with the remaining players.{NOTE:残った人達で何とかしなければ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:18.29,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:917542,918292}All right.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:35.47,Alternative,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:930638,935476}Captain's pace is usually a sign of the whole team's performance.{NOTE:キャプテンの作るペースでチーム全体は実力を出す消すバレーには多いわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:37.64,Alternative,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:935476,937645}Assume all of them are good players.{NOTE:全体を相手にすべきじゃない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.64,0:15:39.85,Alternative,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:937645,939856}You should become their captain.{NOTE:あなたがキャプテンになるべきよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.85,0:15:42.90,Alternative,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:939856,942900}The team no longer needs us second years.{NOTE:二年生の私達はもう必要じゃないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:53.82,Default,Oonuma's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:950241,953828}Miyuki told me she's going out for a walk a while ago.{NOTE:みゆきはその辺に散歩に行くって言ってさっき出たんですよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.82,0:15:56.28,Default,Oonuma's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:953828,956289}She looks troubled.{NOTE:何かこの頃元気がなくって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:15:58.41,Default,Oonuma's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:956289,958416}Did something happen at school?{NOTE:学校で何かあったんでしょうか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:16:00.12,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:958416,960126}No, everything's fine.{NOTE:いいえ、何もありませんわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.12,0:16:02.17,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:960126,962170}I'll look around for her.{NOTE:私この辺を探してみます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.92,0:16:08.88,Default,Child,0,0,0,,{TIME:967925,968885}This way!{NOTE:こっちよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:10.30,Default,Child,0,0,0,,{TIME:968885,970303}Come on!{NOTE:こっちこい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:18.72,Default,Child,0,0,0,,{TIME:976767,978728}Tell us about volleyball, miss!{NOTE:お姉ちゃん、バレーを教えて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:20.18,Default,Child,0,0,0,,{TIME:978728,980188}Please!{NOTE:ね、お願いよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:21.23,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:980188,981230}Sure.{NOTE:うん。いいわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:24.98,Default,Child,0,0,0,,{TIME:982815,984984}Let's play, let's play!{NOTE:さ、やろうやろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:27.73,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:986527,987737}Good, good!{NOTE:上手い、上手い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:29.03,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:987737,989030}You got a whole lot better!{NOTE:だいぶ上手く成ったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:30.44,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:989030,990448}Keep it up, keep it up.{NOTE:その調子、その調子。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:31.86,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:990448,991866}Here goes next one.{NOTE:さ、次行くわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:36.49,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:993409,996496}Great. Stretch your arms straight out.{NOTE:そう、腕を真っ直ぐに伸ばすともっといわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:40.24,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:998539,1000249}Keep your eyes on the ball.{NOTE:ボールから目を放しちゃ駄目よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:42.37,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000249,1002376}Try to accept the ball sooner.{NOTE:もっと前に出てボールを取らなきゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:45.46,Default,Child,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003586,1005463}Oops, I forgot.{NOTE:いけない。忘れてた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:49.00,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007340,1009008}Okay, let's go.{NOTE:はい、行くわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:50.63,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009008,1010635}Good, keep it up!{NOTE:そう。その調子。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.63,0:16:52.01,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010635,1012011}You're doing great!{NOTE:うん！上手い！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:53.26,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012762,1013262}Come on!{NOTE:ほら！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:56.43,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014972,1016432}Stretch your arms!{NOTE:腕を伸ばして！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:00.93,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019560,1020937}Good, good.{NOTE:そうよ、そうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:02.31,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020937,1022313}Let's wrap it up for today.{NOTE:はい、今日はここまで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:04.39,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022313,1024398}It's getting dark, so hurry up home.{NOTE:暗くなるからもうおかえりなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:06.90,Default,Child,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025316,1026901}Teach us more next time!{NOTE:又今度教えて！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:07.81,Default,Child,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026901,1027818}Good bye!{NOTE:さようなら！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:09.86,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027818,1029862}Good bye! Till next time!{NOTE:さようなら！又今度ね！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:11.23,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029862,1031239}Be safe on your way home!{NOTE:気をつけて帰るのよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:12.03,Default,Child,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031239,1032031}Okay!{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.19,0:17:14.20,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033199,1034200}Aren't you going to her?{NOTE:早く行かないのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:17.20,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035952,1037203}Ah, Tsutomu-kun.{NOTE:あ、努くん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:20.08,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038120,1040081}What are you doing?\NAren't you going to her?{NOTE:何してるんだ？早く行かないのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:21.45,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040665,1041457}Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:23.54,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041457,1043543}You came to pick Captain Oonuma up, didn't you?{NOTE:大沼キャプテンを迎えに来たんだろう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:24.79,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043543,1044794}How did you know?{NOTE:どうしてそれが？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:27.46,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044794,1047463}I know the way you think.{NOTE:分かるよ。君が何を考えているかは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.96,0:17:32.05,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049966,1052051}Hurry up and tell her what you want to.{NOTE:さ。早く行って言いたいこと言うんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:35.30,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054345,1055304}Yeah.{NOTE:え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:36.72,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055304,1056722}Believe in yourself, Kozue-kun.{NOTE:しっかりな、こずえくん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:38.43,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056722,1058432}I'm in the middle of delivery.\NI'll be on my way.{NOTE:じゃ、僕は配達の途中だから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:48.06,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067108,1068067}Thank you.{NOTE:有難う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:50.94,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069735,1070945}Oonuma-san!{NOTE:大沼さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:52.40,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071612,1072405}Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:55.11,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073489,1075116}Oonuma-san!{NOTE:大沼さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:59.24,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076617,1079245}Captain, I'd like to ask you\Nto return to our volleyball club.{NOTE:お願いしますキャプテン、バレー部に戻って来てください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:00.70,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079245,1080705}Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:03.49,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080705,1083499}Right now the Fujimi High School team\Ndoesn't deserve its name.{NOTE:今のバレー部は富士見高校のチームとは言えません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.49,0:18:05.45,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083499,1085459}Please, get back.{NOTE:お願いです。戻って来てください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:07.87,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085459,1087878}Make us into a proper Fujimi High School team.{NOTE:そして富士見高校のチームを作ってください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:19.22,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097471,1099223}The club room is lonely without you.{NOTE:部室が寂しくなっています。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:22.47,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099223,1102476}Everyone misses their captain that showed at the club every day for two years.{NOTE:キャプテンが二年以上も毎日だ物質が寂しがっています。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.81,0:18:26.93,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103811,1106939}I haven't been enrolled for a single month yet.{NOTE:私何か未だ一ヶ月も立っていません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.93,0:18:29.56,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106939,1109567}I've no idea how to comfort them.{NOTE:どうして慰めたらいいのか分かりません。}
